{"word":"G2577 - κάμνω - kámnō - kam'-no - Faint","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κάμνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kámnō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kam'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Faint</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சோர்ந்துபோ, பிணியாயிரு, இளைப்படை"},{"paragraph":"1. to grow weary, be weary"},{"paragraph":"2. to be sick"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently a primary verb; properly to <i>toil</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>tire</i> (figuratively <i>faint</i>, <i>sicken</i>): - faint, sicken, be wearied.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}